res-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x61CC;</span></a><a href="/whv/嶧"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5DA7;</span></a><a href="/whv/嬕"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x5B15;</span></a><a href="/whv/墿"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x58BF;</span></a><a href="/whv/凙"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x51D9;</span></a><a href="/whv/睪"><span class="hvres-variant han" data-tippy-placement="bottom">&#x776A;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>
